s/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lizzo-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Lizzo">Lizzo</a>分享了她即将发行的专辑“ Love In Real Life”中毫无歉意的新单曲“ Still Bad”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">lizzo  - “特别”评论：自信，自我授权的bops的快乐超级巨星升起</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌的特色是80年代风格的钥匙和头像拍手，而Lizzo表明她仍然像以往任何时候一样毫无歉意。 <em>“我不需要他。我需要喝一杯</em>。然后她喊道： <em>“毕竟，我仍然生存，我仍然很糟糕，宝贝，所以我不能抱怨。”</em></p><p> Lizzo以前在她的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG363mASsWz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=embed_video_watch_again" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram上有一个视频剪辑在她的跳舞和唱歌的曲目</a>上嘲笑“仍然很糟糕”，同时又唱着卷发和全红色的合奏。剪辑的位置标签为“您的新喜爱歌曲”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="仍然很糟糕" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T1mxODoiz3I?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “仍然很糟糕”标志着Lizzo即将发行的第五张专辑《现实生活中的Love In Real》的第二个品尝者。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-music-video-for-lizzos-funky-indie-rock-comeback-single-love-in-real-life-3842164">之前发布了LP的冠军头单曲</a>。这张专辑的主打单曲Mark Mark Lizzo自2022年LP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">Specia</a> L”以来重返音乐。在撰写本文时，“现实生活中的爱”没有正式发布日期。新闻稿分享说：“本章全部涉及爱，生活和利佐。”</p><p>尼克·莱文（Nick Levine）在对“特别”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lizzo-special-review-joyful-superstar-uplifts-with-self-assured-self-empowering-bops-3270388">四星级评论</a>中为<em>NME</em>写道：“也许不可避免地，考虑到Lizzo的压倒性积极信息，“ Special”有时会有些俗气。尽管如此，它还是不想抗拒的方式俗气的。 “<em>是你的生日吗，女孩？ /“因为你看起来像礼物</em>，”她在“生日女孩”上唱歌，这首歌几乎将您前进到酒吧，并向您命令您拍摄龙舌兰酒玫瑰的照片。</p><p> “在这个证据上，Lizzo确切地知道她是一名艺术家以及她想实现的目标：她是一个坏母狗，拥有令人难以置信的才华，使人们感觉良好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHG0a93vrEu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,