0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Lucy-Dacus">露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus）</a>分享了即将发行的专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-new-album-forever-is-a-feeling-two-powerful-singles-us-tour-3829267">永远的感觉</a>”中脆弱的新单曲“ Talk”。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/boygenius-the-record-nme-album-of-the-year-2023-3555857">Boygenius关于“记录”的持久力量：“我们感觉就像我们希望的一样好”</a></strong></li></ul><p>当Dacus问： <em>“我们为什么不再说话 /我们曾经说话了几个小时 /我会让您紧张或无聊 /或我喝了您的最后一滴，</em> ”曲目以打击的鼓声和模糊的吉他为特色。”</p><p> “ Talk”标志着她即将发行的第四张专辑将发行的第四张单曲，该专辑将于3月28日通过Polydor/Geffen（<a href="https://lucydacus.lnk.to/foreverisafeeling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预先保存</a>）发行。该曲目遵循先前共享的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-new-album-forever-is-a-feeling-two-powerful-singles-us-tour-3829267">“踝关节”和“灰色”（两者都在一月份到达</a>）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-shares-new-anthem-for-queer-tenderness-best-guess-and-announces-2025-uk-and-european-tour-listen-buy-tickets-3837051">上个月的“最佳猜测”</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="露西·达克斯（Lucy Dacus） - 谈话（官方抒情视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dhKTYG5cpc0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-reveals-tracklist-for-upcoming-album-forever-is-a-feeling-3845201#">透露了“永远的感觉”的13首曲目列表</a>，其中包括妮可·雅克琳·史密斯（Nicole Jaclyn Smith）的定制插图。</p><p>在尚未听到的剩下的10条曲目中，有专辑揭幕战&#39;Calliope Prelude&#39;，&#39;Modigliani&#39;，标题曲目“ Forever是一种感觉”，“最想要的人”和“迷失的时间”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hozier">Hozier</a>还将出现在专辑中，即曲目“ Bullseye”。</p><p>尽管<a href="/artists/hozier">Hozier</a>是迄今为止唯一列出的特色嘉宾，但此前据报道，该唱片将包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-mills">Blake Mills</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bartees-strange">Bartees Strange</a> ，Madison Cunningham，Collin Pastore，Jake Finch和Melina Duterte的贡献。据报道，达科斯的<a href="/artists/Boygenius">Boygenius</a>乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里德格斯（Phoebe Bridgers）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）</a>也将露面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHB8h8WSRFK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g tra