head-chappell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-amazons">亚马逊人</a>在他们称之为“我的扭结”的歌曲中分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">广播电台（Radiohead）</a>的混搭。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-interview-pitch-black-21st-century-fiction-royal-blood-politics-masculinity-3809874">他们的新专辑中的亚马逊以及为什么“小说”可能是“ 21世纪的定义词之一”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该录音是在本周早些时候在BBC Radio 1举行的一次非常特别的Maida Vale会议上完成的，并且预计他们即将发行的第四张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-announce-intimate-december-2024-21st-century-prologue-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3810543">“ 21世纪小说”。</a></p><p>在曲目中，乐队将Chappell Roan曲目“ My Kink Is Karma”与经典的Radiohead Hit命中“ Creep”融合在一起，并将自己的旋转放在这两个上。</p><p>随着混搭，乐队捕捉到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">前<em>NME</em> Cover Star</a>的单曲的同样的情感和通风 - 这是她大型首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">《中西部公主的兴起和堕落》</a>中的第二首曲目。他们还捕捉到与1992年摇滚经典赛中所见的内省和忧郁感。</p><p>他们作为BBC Sounds的一部分分享了Radio 1的完整会议，Maida Vale的露面也看到他们表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-team-up-with-royal-blood-for-raucous-new-single-my-blood-3827652">皇家血液协作曲目“ My Blood”</a>的表演，以及他们的热门歌曲“ Love Is Love Is to Dog来自地狱”。</p><p>在下面查看Chappell Roan和Radiohead Mash-up的片段，或<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m0028gds" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>收听BBC的完整声音。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHHHqLiMnb6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 